oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wilma Lee Cooper Metal Photoplate Proof
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Cooper, Wilma Lee, 1921-2011;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two black and white halftone portraits one of an unidentified band and one of Wilma Lee Cooper with a guitar. They are probably the proofs for the metal photoplates made from the original photos. To view a poster that features the metal photoplate for Wilma Lee Cooper, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/31048.
